name: Nanny's Diary
info: Nanny's Diary is an app made for the in-home caretaker. Easily it connects you with all the parents in one forum where you can interact. This application is still a work in progress. Next steps are to add a scheduling calender for the caretaker.

name: Anthym
info: An application built to help orgainze someones daily schedule. The user is able to add, update, save, and delete tasks within the app.

name: Team Profile Generator
info: This application produces an html webpage with your team members rendered on it. The individual cards are based off of what you inputed using Inquirer.

name: Flight Assistant
info: Travel Assistant is a rental finding app that allows people to search for AirbnB rentals using their flight information. The app then uses mutiple API's to populate avaiable AirbnB rentals around your arrival airport.

name: Employee Inquiry
info: Employee Inquiry is a back end application for building and maintaining the employee database of a company. This application can be a foundation to start on and will scale with company growth.

name: Work Day Scheduler
info: An application built to help orgainze someones daily schedule. The user is able to add, update, save, and delete tasks within the app.  .
